   "source": [
    "Our first iteration was successful! Let's try a more complex example."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### The second six-steps interaction\n",
    "\n",
    "We'll just add more complexity without any particular meaning, we can be creative!"
